    public class ISubMatcher
extends fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.impl.ObjectAlignment
implements org.semanticweb.owl.align.AlignmentProcess
    This string matcher implements the iSub string matching algorithm written by Stolios et al in the paper "A String Metric for Ontology Alignment".
    Author:
    audunvennesland 2. feb. 2017
